wikipedia.org/wiki/Syriac_Assembly_Movement","retrieved":1782126848891},{"title":"Natasha Pickowicz (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that New York–based pastry chef <b><a href=\"/wiki/Natasha_Pickowicz\" title=\"Natasha Pickowicz\">Natasha Pickowicz</a></b> wrote a cookbook on Chinese hot pot?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natasha_Pickowicz","retrieved":1782126848892},{"title":"Ōtari-Wilton's Bush (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/%C5%8Ctari-Wilton%27s_Bush\" title=\"Ōtari-Wilton's Bush\">Ōtari-Wilton's Bush</a></b> is the only public botanic garden in New Zealand that is entirely dedicated to native plants?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C5%8Ctari-Wilton%27s_Bush","retrieved":1782126848894},{"title":"1965 Michigan State Spartans football team (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that eight players from the national-champion <b><a href=\"/wiki/1965_Michigan_State_Spartans_football_team\" title=\"1965 Michigan State Spartans football team\">1965 Michigan State Spartans football team</a></b>, including MVP <b><a href=\"/wiki/Steve_Juday\" title=\"Steve Juday\">Steve Juday</a></b>, received first-team <a href=\"/wiki/All-America_college_football_team\" title=\"All-America college football team\">All-America</a> honors?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1965_Michigan_State_Spartans_football_team","retrieved":1782126848895},{"title":"Saint Sadalberga (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Sadalberga\" title=\"Sadalberga\">Saint Sadalberga</a></b> used telepathy to \"order lettuce from her gardener\", according to a story from her <i><a href=\"/wiki/Hagiography\" title=\"Hagiography\">vita</a></i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sadalberga","retrieved":1782126848896},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<span class=\"mw-empty-elt\" about=\"#mwt8\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\" i